---
import SectionHeader from '@/components/section-header.astro';
---
<section class="al-section section" id="about">
  <SectionHeader num="01" title="About" subtitle="A short transmission" accent="amber" />
  <div class="al-about-body body">
    <p class="al-about-lead lead">
      Twenty years of building on the web &mdash; as engineer, designer, sometimes both at
      once. I sit at the seam where <span class="hl">art meets programming</span>:
      where a typeface decision becomes a render budget, where a model&rsquo;s confidence
      becomes an interface, where a deploy pipeline carries someone&rsquo;s intent intact.
    </p>
    <p class="al-about-body2 body2">
      Currently in Vienna, on the Tosca Cloud team at Tricentis. My focus is
      <span class="hl">governance and platform</span> &mdash; monorepo orchestration,
      architectural standards, observability, the rails other teams build on. I also
      build on those rails myself: interfaces and features, hands still in the code.
    </p>
    <div class="al-about-meta-row meta-row">
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-k">Based</div>
        <div class="meta-v">Vienna, Austria</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-k">Mode</div>
        <div class="meta-v">Remote / Hybrid</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-k">Languages</div>
        <div class="meta-v">IT &middot; EN</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-k">Status</div>
        <div class="meta-v status">&#9679; In orbit &mdash; quietly building</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 80px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin: 0;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .hl {
    color: var(--gold-hi);
    font-weight: 500;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 60%, rgba(232,161,58,0.18) 60%);
    padding: 0 4px;
  }
  .body2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin: 0;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .meta-row {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    margin-top: 24px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .meta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .meta-k {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
  }
  .meta-v {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--fg);
  }
  .status { color: var(--sage); }
</style>
